name: Ricky Iwasaki
title: Unjiniyela Wesoftware
summary: Unjiniyela Wesoftware Onolwazi, ofuna ithuba elisha lokusebenzela amaphrojekthi amakhulu. Unentshisekelo yokudala noma yokwengeza ikhodi ezosetshenziswa abanye. Ngikholelwa ukuthi amakhono ami mancane uma kuqhathaniswa ne-inthanethi, ngakho-ke nginesithakazelo esikhulu ekusebenzeni namanye amathuluzi, izinsizakalo, izilimi zokuhlela.

experience.title: Unjiniyela Wesoftware
responsibilities: Kwakhiwe futhi kwasetshenziswa izinhlelo zokusebenza zewebhu ezingakala kusetshenziswa i-React ne-Node.js
Isebenzisana nabaphathi bomkhiqizo ukuze kucwengwe izimfuneko nokuqinisekisa ukulethwa okufika ngesikhathi
Kuthuthukiswe futhi kwagcinwa ama-RESTful API wezinhlelo zokusebenza zewebhu
Imibhalo ethuthukisiwe yokwenza imisebenzi ngokuzenzakalelayo futhi ithuthukise ukusebenza kahle

experience.title: Umsizi Womqeqeshi Wethenisi
responsibilities: Ukufundisa amasu ethenisi kusethingi yeqembu labadlali abangu-5-10
Ukwenza isifundo sibe mnandi futhi sijabulise abadlali
Ibhekele ukuphepha kwabadlali enkundleni, ikakhulukazi abadlali abancane nabadala, abafana nabaneminyaka emi-3 nabaneminyaka engama-60 ubudala.

experience.title: Umngane Ophumayo
responsibilities: Ukugcina indawo ephephile nenobungane kumakhasimende nabasebenzi

projects.name: Iphothifoliyo
projects.description: Iwebhusayithi ephendulayo ekhombisa amaphrojekthi namakhono isebenzisa ubuchwepheshe bewebhu besimanje
